                🔴📝 kernel_matrix ▶️🔧 compute_kernel_matrix data,
                🔴📝 centered_kernel ▶️🔧 center_kernel_matrix kernel_matrix,
                🔴📝 eigenvalues ▶️🔧 quantum_eigenvalue_solver centered_kernel,
